I'm using the "advanced search form" only for search by collection not for =
"item type". We group the informaction resources by collection like:

Colecci=F3n regional (History of Baja related books)
Colecci=F3n UIA-ITESO (Books published by the members of Universidad Iberoa=
mericana in Mexico)
etc., etc.

